body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background: #f4f6f8;
}

/* Navbar */
.navbar {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 15px 40px;
    background: #0a2540;
    color: white;
}

.navbar ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
}

.navbar li {
    margin-left: 20px;
    cursor: pointer;
}

/* Hero */
.hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 80px 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #1e3c72, #2a5298);
    color: white;
}

.hero button {
    padding: 12px 25px;
    background: #ff9800;
    border: none;
    font-size: 16px;
    cursor: pointer;
}

/* Scan Section */
.scan {
    padding: 40px;
    text-align: center;
}

.scan input, .scan textarea {
    width: 60%;
    padding: 10px;
    margin: 10px 0;
}

.scan button {
    padding: 10px 20px;
    background: #1e3c72;
    color: white;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
}

/* Footer */
footer {
    background: #0a2540;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 10px;
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Features - Apkonic</title>

    <style>
        body{
            margin:0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(to right,#0a1931,#1f3c88);
            color:white;
            padding:50px 20px;
        }

        h1{
            text-align:center;
            margin-bottom:50px;
        }

        .feature-container{
            max-width:1100px;
            margin:auto;
            display:flex;
            flex-direction:column;
            gap:30px;
        }

        .feature-card{
            background:white;
            color:black;
            padding:30px;
            border-radius:15px;
            box-shadow:0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            transition:0.3s;
        }

        .feature-card:hover{
            transform:translateY(-5px);
        }

        .feature-card h2{
            margin-bottom:15px;
            color:#1f3c88;
        }

        .feature-card p{
            line-height:1.6;
            font-size:15px;
        }

        .back-btn{
            display:block;
            width:200px;
            text-align:center;
            margin:50px auto 0;
            padding:12px;
            background:#00c3ff;
            color:black;
            border-radius:8px;
            text-decoration:none;
            font-weight:bold;
        }

        .back-btn:hover{
            background:#00aaff;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Features of Apkonic</h1>

<div class="feature-container">

    <div class="feature-card">
        <h2>🔐 Advanced APK Malware Detection</h2>
        <p>
            Apkonic analyzes uploaded APK files to detect potentially malicious behavior. 
            The system checks file size, extension validation, and suspicious indicators 
            to determine whether an application may pose a security threat.
        </p>
        <p>
            This feature helps users avoid installing harmful applications that may steal 
            personal data, banking credentials, or sensitive information.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
        <h2>📱 Smishing (SMS Phishing) Detection</h2>
        <p>
            Apkonic scans SMS messages for phishing keywords such as "bank", "OTP", 
            "urgent", "winner", "lottery", and more.
        </p>
        <p>
            If suspicious content is detected, the system flags the message as a 
            potential SMISHING attack, helping users avoid scam links and fraud attempts.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
        <h2>🛡 Sender Verification System</h2>
        <p>
            The Sender Verification module checks whether an SMS sender ID matches 
            known trusted banking and payment service identifiers such as SBI, HDFC, 
            ICICI, Paytm, and others.
        </p>
        <p>
            Unknown or suspicious senders are flagged to alert users before they 
            trust or respond to the message.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
        <h2>⚡ Fast & Lightweight Processing</h2>
        <p>
            Apkonic is designed to deliver quick results with minimal processing time. 
            The lightweight backend ensures fast scanning without heavy system resource usage.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
        <h2>📊 Clear & User-Friendly Results</h2>
        <p>
            Results are displayed in a clear and understandable format:
            <br><br>
            ✅ SAFE MESSAGE / SAFE APK  
            <br>
            ⚠ SMISHING MESSAGE / Suspicious APK  
        </p>
        <p>
            This helps users quickly understand the risk level and take appropriate action.
        </p>
    </div>

</div>

<a href="/" class="back-btn">⬅ Back to Home</a>

</body>
</html>
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>About Us - Apkonic</title>

    <style>
        body{
            margin:0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(to right,#0a1931,#1f3c88);
            color:white;
            padding:50px 20px;
        }

        h1{
            text-align:center;
            margin-bottom:40px;
        }

        .container{
            max-width:1000px;
            margin:auto;
            display:flex;
            flex-direction:column;
            gap:30px;
        }

        .card{
            background:white;
            color:black;
            padding:30px;
            border-radius:15px;
            box-shadow:0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        .card h2{
            color:#1f3c88;
            margin-bottom:15px;
        }

        .card p{
            line-height:1.6;
            font-size:15px;
        }

        .back-btn{
            display:block;
            width:200px;
            text-align:center;
            margin:50px auto 0;
            padding:12px;
            background:#00c3ff;
            color:black;
            border-radius:8px;
            text-decoration:none;
            font-weight:bold;
        }

        .back-btn:hover{
            background:#00aaff;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<h1>About Apkonic</h1>

<div class="container">

    <div class="card">
        <h2>📌 Project Introduction</h2>
        <p>
            Apkonic is a web-based security system developed to detect fraudulent APK files 
            and smishing (SMS phishing) attacks. The platform is designed to protect users 
            from malicious applications and scam messages that can compromise personal 
            and financial information.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <h2>⚠ Problem Statement</h2>
        <p>
            With the rapid growth of digital banking and online services, cyber fraud 
            has significantly increased. Many users unknowingly install malicious APK files 
            or click on phishing SMS links, resulting in data theft and financial loss. 
            There is a need for a simple and accessible system that helps users identify 
            such threats before damage occurs.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <h2>🎯 Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
            Our mission is to create a safer digital environment by providing a 
            lightweight, fast, and user-friendly detection system that identifies 
            suspicious applications and scam messages in real-time.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <h2>🛠 Technologies Used</h2>
        <p>
            • Python (Flask Framework)<br>
            • HTML5 & CSS3<br>
            • JavaScript (Fetch API)<br>
            • Keyword-based phishing detection logic<br>
            • File validation and size analysis<br>
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <h2>⚙ How It Works</h2>
        <p>
            1. User uploads an APK file or enters an SMS message.<br>
            2. The system analyzes file properties and phishing keywords.<br>
            3. Suspicious indicators are detected.<br>
            4. The system displays a clear SAFE or WARNING result instantly.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <h2>🚀 Future Enhancements</h2>
        <p>
            • Integration with Machine Learning models for advanced detection<br>
            • Real-time database of malicious APK signatures<br>
            • Cloud deployment and API integration<br>
            • Admin dashboard for monitoring threats<br>
        </p>
    </div>

</div>

<a href="/" class="back-btn">⬅ Back to Home</a>

</body>
</html>s
